00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:19,460
So, Jiang Shiyan turned you down,

136
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:21,530
or rather,

137
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:23,520
he's currently not

138
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:24,510
considering working

139
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:25,410
