152
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:49,700
like company structure

153
00:06:49,910 --> 00:06:51,590
and selecting

154
00:06:51,590 --> 00:06:52,730
underwriters.

155
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,900
But this sounds more like

156
00:06:55,270 --> 00:06:57,100
Feng Weiran's area of expertise.

157
00:06:59,270 --> 00:07:00,410
Ultimately, the decision

158
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,820
