163
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:12,850
I understand.

164
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,910
But I'm not a partner

165
00:07:14,910 --> 00:07:16,150
at Yixiu.

166
00:07:16,150 --> 00:07:17,460
I can't help you.

167
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:21,490
Given your professional background,

168
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,600
you should understand

169
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,730
our value better,

170
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:26,170
