173
00:07:43,470 --> 00:07:45,610
It's true that I'm his friend,

174
00:07:46,150 --> 00:07:48,080
but his company has gotten this far

175
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:49,080
thanks to his team,

176
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,170
partners,

