00:07:50,470 --> 00:07:51,390
his decision-making,

178
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:52,930
and his understanding of the market.

179
00:07:54,150 --> 00:07:55,780
You're overestimating my influence.

180
00:08:00,230 --> 00:08:01,460
Everyone thinks

181
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:03,660
I've dated Jiang Shiyan,

182
