00:08:10,030 --> 00:08:10,920
At that time,

184
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,660
I was planning to study abroad.

185
00:08:13,030 --> 00:08:14,350
One day, I bumped into Jiang

186
00:08:14,350 --> 00:08:15,680
