187
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,970
We had a meal together,

188
00:08:17,230 --> 00:08:19,230
and I dragged him to watch a movie,

189
00:08:19,230 --> 00:08:20,820
where we ran into Zhang Tong.

190
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,290
They misunderstood us.

191
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,930
During that time,

192
00:08:25,590 --> 00:08:26,930
you weren't in Rongcheng.

193
00:08:27,230 --> 00:08:28,100
I was

194
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:30,170
feeling sentimental about the city

195
00:08:30,390 --> 00:08:31,470
because I was

196
00:08:31,470 --> 00:08:32,560
about to leave.

197
00:08:32,560 --> 00:08:34,940
So, I kept asking Jiang Shiyan

198
00:08:35,110 --> 00:08:36,490
to hang out with me.

199
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,610
But I noticed,

200
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,420
when he ate something tasty,

201
00:08:41,560 --> 00:08:43,180
he wanted to bring you to try it first.

202
00:08:43,710 --> 00:08:45,010
When he watched a good movie,

203
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,730
he wanted to show it to you first.

204
00:08:47,230 --> 00:08:48,400
When the two of us went out,

205
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,940
it always felt like you were there.

206
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:57,340
It wasn't fun for me at all.

207
00:08:58,590 --> 00:09:00,370
When I left,

208
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,180
I didn't tell him,

209
00:09:02,990 --> 00:09:03,870
and he didn't offer

210
00:09:03,870 --> 00:09:04,890
to see me off.

211
00:09:05,990 --> 00:09:07,180
In the end,

212
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,420
we just drifted apart.

213
00:09:10,470 --> 00:09:12,060
You might not realize

214
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:14,010
how important you are

215
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,130
to him.

216
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:26,250
I've been close to Jiang Shiyan

217
00:09:27,110 --> 00:09:28,940
for so many years.

218
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:31,800
But we've never interfered

219
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:33,730
with each other's decisions.

220
00:09:34,750 --> 00:09:35,890
I fully support

221
00:09:36,350 --> 00:09:37,580
whatever he wants to do,

222
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:40,010
and I would never force him

223
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:42,700
to do things he doesn't like.

224
00:09:44,230 --> 00:09:45,750
If he sees value

225
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:47,200
in working with your law firm,

226
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,370
he'll choose to collaborate.

227
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,240
But if he says

228
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,650
he's not considering it now,

229
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:53,610
then he genuinely isn't.

230
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:55,920
If you think

231
00:09:55,920 --> 00:09:56,920
he rejected you because

232
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:58,650
he didn't see the value in your firm,

233
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:01,060
it just means you don't understand him.

234
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:03,060
Or perhaps

235
00:10:04,830 --> 00:10:07,010
you're not suited to be his partner.

236
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,610
Let me give you an example.

237
00:10:16,510 --> 00:10:18,420
Maybe two years ago.

238
00:10:18,680 --> 00:10:20,200
Yixiu's food video team

239
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,700
once produced a video

240
00:10:21,920 --> 00:10:23,460
that had two parts.

241
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,320
The first part was

242
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,510
about a well-known restaurant

243
00:10:27,510 --> 00:10:29,490
being reported
for using bad ingredients.

244
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:30,800
The second part,

245
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:32,250
after their investigation,

246
00:10:32,370 --> 00:10:33,220
revealed that place

247
00:10:33,230 --> 00:10:34,770
wasn't using bad ingredients.

248
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:37,340
The video team thought

249
00:10:37,510 --> 00:10:38,510
of airing the first part

250
00:10:38,510 --> 00:10:40,320
to grab attention

251
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,970
and the second part for the twist.

252
00:10:43,110 --> 00:10:44,970
But Jiang Shiyan was furious.

253
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:47,460
He said, "Have you thought"

254
00:10:47,630 --> 00:10:49,700
"about how the restaurant's owner"

255
00:10:49,830 --> 00:10:51,490
"would suffer"

256
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:53,370
"after just the first part airs?"

257
00:10:53,870 --> 00:10:54,720
"By the time"

258
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:55,670
"the second part airs,"

259
00:10:55,670 --> 00:10:57,420
"the restaurant might already
be destroyed."

260
00:10:57,830 --> 00:10:59,240
So, he demanded that the team

261
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,420
re-edit it,

262
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:02,460
and they had to reveal the truth first.

263
00:11:03,470 --> 00:11:04,960
If you've carefully studied Yixiu,

264
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:06,130
you'll notice

265
00:11:06,350 --> 00:11:07,870
that in Yixiu's food reviews,

266
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:09,680
it's not only the popular influencers

267
00:11:09,680 --> 00:11:10,940
who get recommended.

268
00:11:11,230 --> 00:11:12,440
Lots of common people's videos

269
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:13,940
also get recommended.

270
00:11:15,350 --> 00:11:16,590
That's because they're never

271
00:11:16,590 --> 00:11:18,300
in a rush to chase after capital.

272
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,240
Their financing

273
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,710
and business expansion

274
00:11:21,710 --> 00:11:22,600
all follow

275
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:24,460
Jiang's own plan and pace.

276
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,250
In short,

277
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:29,890
I really can't help you

278
00:11:30,750 --> 00:11:32,100
with this.

279
00:11:37,990 --> 00:11:39,750
I once told Jiang Shiyan

280
00:11:39,750 --> 00:11:40,730
that I envied you.

281
00:11:41,470 --> 00:11:42,370
But now,

282
00:11:43,280 --> 00:11:44,490
I envy him.

283
00:11:49,830 --> 00:11:51,110
Back in high school,

284
00:11:51,110 --> 00:11:52,160
why didn't we become

285
00:11:52,160 --> 00:11:53,180
good friends?

286
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:58,080
We can still become

287
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,220
good friends now.

288
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:04,560
I didn't manage to secure

289
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:06,220
my most promising client,

